text: LOCALWaves crash into the Ventura Pier Thursday, Dec. 28, 2023, during high surf conditions.CONTRIBUTED PHOTO/ERIC BOLDTFaria Beach in Ventura gets slammed with waves Thursday, Dec. 28, 2023.
